{"tid":2266890,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"安帥賽後落鑊慘食無情雞","createTime":"2020-11-01T16:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T16:53:41.000Z","uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a0194dc10f40bb0955c7d0eef635cccac4cb3e08","tid":2266890,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T16:02:03.000Z","msg":"拿玻里周二晚於主場大勝亨克4︰0，取得E組次名出線權，亦是球隊自2016/17球季後再次晉級16強。不過拿玻里在今仗之前經歷9場不勝，於意甲榜僅排第7位，落後榜首的國米17分。<br />\n<br />\n因此在獲勝後僅1小時，球會便宣佈解僱安察洛堤，但聲明表示基於友誼及共識，他與主席勞倫迪爾斯的友好關係不變。而「肥安」被炒後，已傳出有望接掌阿仙奴及愛華頓帥印。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh1gnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=0412ee59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32b33c45d0745d57331611434e2a7fa76aaeb9e","tid":2266890,"uid":44285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T16:12:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9adc14e1b048317db92136f7b0c60fb157918034","tid":2266890,"uid":322766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T16:12:50.000Z","msg":"Old news"},{"pid":"b479dcf7baca667c02f345745c8404562ab4c581","tid":2266890,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T16:53:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}